<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Our Inspiration </title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --navy: #1a2a6c;
            --accent-blue: #4a90e2;
            --text-gray: #555;
            --bg-light: #f8f9fa;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #dee2e6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }

        /* SECTION 1 Styling */
        .inspiration-card {
            background: white; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); margin-bottom: 40px;
            display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .inspiration-header { background: var(--navy); color: white; padding: 20px 40px; width: 100%; }

        .image-col {
            flex: 1; min-width: 300px; padding: 40px; background: #f1f3f5;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        }

        /* Photo Frame for Aditya Nath */
        .profile-img {
            width: 220px; height: 280px; object-fit: cover;
            border: 8px solid white; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            border-radius: 4px; background: #ccc; /* Placeholder color */
        }

        .content-col { flex: 2; min-width: 350px; padding: 40px; line-height: 1.7; text-align: justify; }

        /* SECTION 2 Styling */
        .chairman-section {
            background: white; border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border-top: 8px solid var(--accent-blue);
        }

        .chairman-flex { display: flex; gap: 30px; margin-bottom: 20px; align-items: flex-start; }

        /* Photo Frame for Current Chairman */
        .chairman-photo-box {
            flex-shrink: 0; width: 250px; border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 10px; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .chairman-photo-box img { width: 100%; border-radius: 4px; display: block; }

        .quote-block {
            background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 15px; padding: 25px;
            margin: 20px 0; font-style: italic; border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-blue);
        }

        .back-btn { display: inline-block; margin-top: 30px; text-decoration: none; color: var(--navy); font-weight: bold; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .inspiration-card, .chairman-flex { flex-direction: column; }
            .chairman-photo-box { width: 100%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    
    <div class="inspiration-card">
        <div class="inspiration-header">
            <h2>Our Inspiration</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="image-col">
            <img src="aditya_nath.jpg" alt="Late Aditya Nath" class="profile-img">
            <div style="margin-top: 15px; text-align: center;">
                <h3 style="margin: 0; color: var(--navy);">ADITYANATH SIR</h3>
                <span style="color: var(--accent-blue); font-weight: bold;">Former Chairman</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content-col">
            <p><strong>Aditya Nath</strong>, the former Chairman of Adwaita Mission group of Institutions, commanded the honour of translating the vision of Late Anand Shankar Madhavan into reality. Under his dynamic stewardship, the Vidyapith progressed leaps and bounds with the establishment and successful functioning of institutions like B.Ed. and D.El.Ed. Colleges, an I.T.I. and an Engineering College.</p>
            <p>Late Aditya Nath was born in Kerala and settled in Bihar where he served the society by opening up new avenues for children and youth. His disciplined life and indomitable will power will ever remain an illuminating inspiration for the whole Vidyapith family.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="chairman-section">
        <div class="chairman-flex">
            <div class="chairman-photo-box">
                <img src="chairman.jpg" alt="Sri Aravindakshan Madambath">
                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;">
                    Sri Aravindakshan Madambath<br>
                    <small style="color: var(--accent-blue);">Chairman</small>
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="chairman-text">
                <h1 style="color: var(--navy); margin-top: 0;">From Chairman's Desk</h1>
                <p>AMHS is dedicated to the pursuit of academic excellence, encouraging students to become independent and perceptive thinkers, confident, enlightened learners and socially responsible citizens.</p>
                <p>We are committed to inculcating in all our students strong ethical values of integrity, respect and discipline as well as clarity in thought and decision making ability.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-block">
            "In order to achieve these, AMHS follows rigorous programme that is based upon the best educational practices, highly progressive and recognized world-wide."
        </div>

        <p>Furthermore, it has been our founder Late Madhavanji’s and former Chairman Late Aditya Nath’s quest in life to make high quality education available and affordable to both the rural and urban as well. AMHS will be the foundation for a new generation of readers and innovators.</p>

        <a href="main.html" class="back-btn">← Back to Dashboard</a>
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
